\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 comes from the fact that this force is has a much smaller effective range
 than the electromagnetic, strong nuclear, and gravitational forces.
 This is due to the weak mediating bosons, the 
\begin_inset Formula $W^{\pm}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

